categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A male Human Jedi lived at some point following the Great Jedi Purge. He publicly claimed a rank of Jedi Master despite knowing it would attract the attention of Darth Vader.
This character was depicted on the "Jedi Master" card of the Champions of the Force, the base set of the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game, which was illustrated by artist Kieran Yanner.
